HEADWORD: Nonresistance
<hw>Non`re*sist"ance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
principles or practice of a nonresistant; passive obedience; submission
to authority, power, oppression, or violence without
opposition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

